m Welch]] |[[Free Foresters Cricket Club|Free Foresters]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33723/33723.html] |25 May 1940 |[[Calais]], France |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2214733] |- |[[Robin Whetherly]] |[[Oxford University Cricket Club|Oxford University]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33773/33773.html] |27 November 1943 |near [[Glamoč]], [[Yugoslavia]] |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2224436] |- |[[Peter Whitehouse]] |[[Oxford University Cricket Club|Oxford University]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33818/33818.html] |19 November 1943 |[[Archi, Italy]] |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2215219] |- |[[John Whitty (cricketer)|John Whitty]] |[[British Army cricket team|Army]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33839/33839.html] |23 October 1944 |[[Vicchio]], [[Florence]], Italy |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2379644] |- |[[Alec Wills]] |[[Combined Services cricket team|Combined Services]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33923/33923.html] |7 November 1941 |[[Kallang]], [[Singapore]] |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2822037] |- |[[Roger Winlaw]] |[[Cambridge University Cricket Club|Cambridge University]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/33/33985/33985.html] |31 October 1942 |[[Caernarfon|Caernarvon]], Wales |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2412034] |- |[[Denys Witherington]] |[[Cambridge University Cricket Club|Cambridge University]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/34/34008/34008.html] |16 February 1944 |near [[Anzio]], Italy |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2678714] |- |[[Barney Wood]] |[[Western Australia cricket team|Western Australia]] |[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/16/16887/16887.html] |9 June 1941 |[[Syria]] |[http://www.cwgc.org/find-war-dead/casualty/2188551] |- |}
